      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAST RUPEE (2) is better than last start when fifth (25.58) in a Grade 4/5 at Grafton over 450m. Has a strong record from box 2, including two wins. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. MRS. JACOBS (3) made light work of a wide draw last time with a strong early sectional and clocking 16.87 in a 0.8 lengths win at this track over 300m. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Hard to fault her form and she makes plenty of appeal. RUDOLF RUMBLE (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Last start finished 4th on February 8 over 350m at Grafton behind Reel 'Em Mini beaten 6 lengths (20.43) in a Grade 4/5. Looks well placed here and among the chances. BACKCREEK BUTCH (5) has definite claims at his first try at this circuit.",
